Global Egg Yolk Lecithin Powder Market Insights
Egg Yolk Lecithin Powder Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Egg Yolk Lecithin Powder Market Overview
The global egg yolk lecithin powder market has witnessed significant growth in recent years, driven by its increasing demand across various industries such as food and beverages, pharmaceuticals, cosmetics, and animal feed. The market size was valued at approximately USD 500 million in 2024 and is projected to grow at a CAGR of 5.5% during the forecast period (2025-2030). Egg yolk lecithin powder is widely used due to its emulsifying, stabilizing, and anti-oxidative properties, making it an essential ingredient in many applications. This growth is also supported by the rising consumer preference for natural and organic ingredients in food products, as well as increased awareness about the health benefits of lecithin.

